Cybil may have been drawn here by someone.[p]
As she nears the elementary school, part of her shirt becomes soaked with clammy sweat.[p]
"Is it really ok to go inside?"[p]
She asks herself this many times.[p]
As she reached the edge of the school grounds, her conscientious sense of duty as a police officer, [p]
rose up within her along with her sense of reason, and she began to walk naturally towards the school.[p]
It is now too late for her to turn back.[p]
She readies herself, and then using both hands, she pushes the door in front of her open with all her strength.[p]


