The aged building reeked of a peculiar mildew.[p]
However, its insides were much cleaner than she had expected, and Cybil found this a bit surprising.[p]
Perhaps it was just the result of her enduring the cold wind for so long, but she had a terrible headache.[p]
Cybil pressed her fingers to her temples, and eventually began to walk aimlessly again.[p]


[tb_hide_message_window  ]
